short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Downloads a SVG version of Logic App workflow.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When working with Azure Logic Apps, Our workflows can get too big and complex to visualize, This tool helps you download a SVG image of the full workflow, You can then take a print out of this or project it on a bigger screen.
